---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 539
  - Title: Devikalottara-Jnanachara-Vichara-Patalam
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Prayer-Meditation-Contemplation=The Oratory of the Heart
  - 152b
  - 532
---
Without allowing the mind to externalize itself and go towards the
objects of the senses, keep it always in its own natural abode or
centre -- the heart. Do not allow it to get attached to external
objects. Keep it steady, free from any oscillation.
